    Brazilian Red List of Plant species

    plantsBRlist.Rd

    Dataset of the official Brazilian Threatened Species List published by the Ministério do Meio Ambiente

    Usage

    plantsBRlist

    Formato

    plantsBRlist

    A data frame with 3209 rows and 4 columns:

    order

    Taxonomic Order

    family

    Taxonomic Family

    species

    Scientific name

    category

    Category of threat

    MMA2014

    Species was evaluated in the past list (2014)

    ...

    Detalhes

    Source availabe at MMA 300/2022
